These are Puzzles for 1x2 Level 5

.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-5-1::.
There are 2 different nationalities: british, dutch
1. the dutch is somewhere to the right of the british##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2   |
| Nationality   | british | dutch |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-5-2::.
The people use 2 different means of transport: train, van
1. the person driving the train is somewhere to the left of the person driving the van##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1   |  2  |
| Transport   | train | van |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-5-3::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: adventure, time-travel
1. the person watching time-travel movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching adventure movies##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |
| Movie-Genre   | time-travel | adventure |

